      "Fixed-fee &middot; written scope in 3 days"
    ],
    "eyebrow": "New York &middot; Small Business",
    "heading": "Your New York <em>small business accountant</em>, starting with the books.",
    "subheading": "Bookkeeping, QuickBooks setup, and cleanup for New York small businesses &mdash; the financial backbone that keeps you organized, compliant, and ready for your CPA. Entity-aware books for LLCs, S-corps, and partnerships, NYC &amp; NY sales-tax tracking, and a named Certified ProAdvisor. We keep the books; your CPA files. Fixed-fee, all 62 counties.",
    "actions": [
