    "source": "Reviewed by the Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team at TechBrot Inc., an independent firm &mdash; not affiliated with Intuit Inc., and not a CPA or tax-prep firm. New York facts (NYC Unincorporated Business Tax; NYC combined 8.875% sales-tax rate) reflect current NYC and NY DTF guidance."
  },
  "ctaBand": {
    "eyebrow": "New York small businesses start here",
    "heading": "Get the books right — the rest gets easier.",
    "lede": "Book a free discovery call. We&rsquo;ll review your situation and your books, recommend setup, cleanup, monthly service, or a mix, and send a written fixed-fee quote within 3 business days. No pitch. Independent firm &mdash; we keep the books and coordinate with your CPA, who files; we do not file NY taxes.",
